Articles.Content: Welcome to another session of Interesting Rocket Designs! Sadly, there was no participants last time so there were no winners.Go ahead and send your interesting rocket designs here! Judging will take place on next saturday at 3:00 EST.

Here is my entry. It is called "Mencius" after the Chinese Philosopher.  It is a top staging rocket, which allows you to only use one engine and still shed weight.

 

Here is the KerbalX link: https://kerbalx.com/Klapaucius/Mencius-Top-Staging-Rocket
Make sure to add something! Contribute to the challenge!
